FIRST COMMANDS - Check for TTY window; start script. If not TTY1, warn user from starting WM/DE

warning() - Create warning screen

slmlogin() - Run a function that creates a TTY-based "display manager"

xorg() - Start an X.Org login prompt. Use local sx script to start Xorg

wayland() - Start a Wayland login prompt

ttyexit () - Exit to TTY
